TITLEFencesSTARRINGDenzel Washington, Viola Davis, Stephen McKinley Henderson, Jovan AdepoGENREDramaRelease DateDecember 25Troy is a garbage collector who harbours a lot of bitterness for the way his life turned out. Troy lives with his wife Rose and their son Cory, although he has another son Lyons, from a previous relationship. Troy has an estranged relationship with his children and somewhat of a resentment for his Cory&rsquo;s football skills. The intense performances of Davis and Washington have stirred up murmurings of Oscar nominations. Washington also takes up the tasking role of director for the film, which is based on the Pulitzer award winning play of the same name.